metadata.name: MTTM#01A
metadata.description:
Limitless, timeless, endless emotions.  
They could be anybody, nobody, everybody,  
Anywhere and everywhere,  
Now, before, and after.  
---  
Are they patients in an asylum? Or maybe enraged inmates in a high-security prison? Maybe both?  
---  
Reflections of my emotions on their faces and in return, their faces trigger emotions in me.

And vice versa.

MIRROR TO THEM | MƎ
